Title: Password field in update section accepts old password.

Description: When i enter old password in the update password then input field accepts it.

Steps to reproduce: Go to "My Account" in the navigation bar then go to "My Addresses" then click on "Update"
and put values in old password,new password,confirm password input field. 

Environment: Google Chrome

Expected results: You can not use your old password as your new password.

Assigned to: Rajoy Chowdhury

Severity: Medium.